	* Makefile.am [ZLIB] (libdwfl_a_SOURCES): Add it.
	* bzip2.c: New file.
	* Makefile.am [BZLIB] (libdwfl_a_SOURCES): Add it.
	* libdwflP.h: Declare __libdw_gunzip, __libdw_bunzip2.

